functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content: List the top 5 fastest animals and their species.
List the top 5 fastest animals and their species.

Here is a list of the top 5 fastest land animals and their species:

1. Peregrine Falcon (Falco peregrinus): The peregrine falcon is the fastest animal on the planet, reaching speeds of up to 240 mph (386 km/h) during its hunting dive, known as a stoop.
2. White-throated Needletail (Hirundapus caudacutus): This bird species can fly at incredible speeds, estimated to be between 69-105 mph (111-169 km/h). It is considered the fastest bird in level flight.
3. Golden Eagle (Aquila chrysaetos): The golden eagle can achieve speeds of over 150 mph (241 km/h) during its hunting dive.
4. White-tailed Deer (Odocoileus virginianus): Running at speeds up to 40 mph (64 km/h), the white-tailed deer is one of the fastest land mammals.
5. Pronghorn (Antilocapra americana): Native to North America, the pronghorn can run at speeds up to 60 mph (96.5 km/h) and maintain a steady pace over long distances.
